            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName>Gurgio</persName> filio bone memorie
                            <persName>Bonitii</persName> vende a <persName key="#Priests"
                            >Leo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filio bone memorie
                            <persName>Iohannis</persName> (…) una <rs key="#Petiae">petia</rs> de
                        terra mea illa quam in loco et finibus <placeName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#places/87">prope <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                            <orgName key="#Churches">Sancti Iusti</orgName></placeName>, quod uno
                        capo tenet in <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Churches">beati Sancti
                            Iusti</orgName>, et alio capo tenet in terra <persName key="#Priests"
                            >Ghisolfi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs> et de <rs
                            key="#Consortes/shared_possessions">consortibus</rs> suis, lato uno
                        tenet in terra <persName>Winigi</persName> et alio lato tenet in terra
                            <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Mother_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/86">Sacti Cerboni</orgName>, con tutte le sue
                        dipendenze, per il prezzo di argentum sol. vihinti in prefinito. Chiede a
                            <orgName key="#Notary">Brondicardi</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notari</rs> domini imperatoris la stesura della cartula.
                        Actum loco <placeName ref="#places/265">Massa</placeName>. Testimoni:
                            <persName>Guntolini</persName> filio bone memorie
                            <persName>Mainti</persName>; <persName>Teuti</persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName>Suaviti</persName>; <persName>Eribaldi</persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName>Petri</persName>. Scrive: Brondicardo notarius domni
                        imperatoris.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
